<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text"><i>Tamarix </i>spp. vigorously sprout after fire, and they increase flowering and seed production after fire. Mixed riparian stands often change to tamarisk-dominated stands after fire (Brooks and Minnich 2006, Zouhar 2003b).</div>
